A Complete Workflow for Team Contributions

Welcome to the project!
This guide explains how to work collaboratively using Git, GitHub, and standard development workflows.

ğŸ“Œ 1. Initial Setup

Before collaborating:

âœ… Install Tools

Git â†’ https://git-scm.com/downloads

VS Code / IntelliJ / PyCharm

Node.js (for frontend)

Python + virtualenv (for backend + GA)

Docker (optional but recommended)

âœ… Configure Git (once)
git config --global user.name "Your Name"
